      <title>How to use Grand Central</title>
      <html>
        <p>Click on the 
          <a href="observation_deck">Observation Deck</a> to see the state of your deployments. 
        </p>
        <p>Use the 
          <a href="grand_central_accounts">Grand Central Accounts</a>, under the "Configure Data Sources" to setup your Cloud accounts for management.
        </p>
        <p>The 
          <a href="pushvpull">Push vs. Pull </a> dashboard can show you the estimated differences in cost of pushing vs. pulling your data into Splunk. 
        </p>
        <p>The last two dashboards, 
          <a href="templates">Template Manager</a>,
          <a href="trumpet">Trumpet AWS Configuration Builder</a> can be used to create and manage custom Cloud Formation templates that you can use with Grand Central.
        </p>
      </html>
